Egyptian Multiplication, must be postive integers

C++ 
int multiply0(int n, int a){
if (n==1) return a;
return multiply0(n-1, a)+a
}

Clojure 

(defn multiply0 
  [n a]
  (loop [i a]
   (when(= i 1)
   (return a)
   (recur (multiply0[n-1,a]))+a  
)

Java
def multiply0(int n, int a){
  if(n==1){
   return a;
  }
  return multiply0(n-1,a)+a;
}
